  1.U7-si5 hiaN-ti7 e5 chhu3 li7 pai3-tng5 khah- hng7, kiam2-chhai2 phou3-goa7 lou7 a2-si7 nng7- phou3 lou7 , in chiu7 ai3 leng7-goa7 chu7-chip8 : taN mng7 khoaN3 eng-kai tioh8 chun2 in khah-ho2 , a2-si7 tioh8 khng3 in tioh8 lai5 pai3- tng5 chu7-chip8 khah-ho2 ? 
  Ng5 Tek-phiau sia2: Goa2 siuN7 chit-e5 su7 put-chi2 oh in3 . Na7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 Sin5 tak8 sou2-chai7 ti7-teh ; chhin-chhiuN7 Ia5-sou in3 Sat-ma2-li7-a e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2 , “ Pai3 Siong7-te3 bo5-lun7 chit-e5 soaN a2-si7 Ia5-lou7- sat-leng2 , iau3-kin2 eng7 seng3-sit8 ”. Koh kong2 , “ Bo5 lun7 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7 nng7 saN lang5 chu7-chip8 , goa2 ia7 kap in ti7-teh ”. Chiau3 an2-ni lai5 lun7 thang chun2 ka-ti7 chu7-chip8 . Tioh8 siuN7 chit-si5 tak8-lang5 sim- seng3 loan2-jiok8, tioh8 bian2-le7 in lai5 le2-pai3-tng5 chiaN3 hap8-sit,boh8-tit chun2 in ka- ti7 chu7-chip8. Lai5 cho3 gou7-hang7. Thau5-chit8-hang7, e7 pin5-toaN7. Te7-ji7, e7 kiau-ngou7 . Te7-saN, e7 ka-ti7 phin2-phong2 . Te7-si3, e7 ka-ti7 cho3 chun-kui3 . Te7-gou7 , e7 biau2-si Seng3- hoe7 , bo5 liah8 cho3 iau3-kin2 . Na7 an2-ni kiam2 bo5 gai7-tioh8 to7-li2 mah ? Tioh8 siuN7 chai7-cha2 Thian-chu2 Ia5-sou nng7 kau3 goan5-thau5 si7 chit8 the2 , lou7-boe2 hun-cho3 nng7 lou7 . Siat-su2 be7-e7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, kiaN-liau2 koan3- siok8 chiaN5 chu7-chu2 e5 kau3.Thang siuN7 Sian-ti Seng3-tou5 ui7-tioh8 chin-to7 phoe-si2 phau2- chau2, hek8-si7 koe3 goa7-kok , hek8-si7 chau2- chhut pat8 hiuN-sia7 , bo5 hiam5 lou7-tou5 e5 hng7 . Ho5-hong3 lan2 ai3 tit-tioh8 chin-to7 , ku2-tng5 e5 hok-khi3, lai5 iuN2-chhi7 bo5 pai7-hoai7 e5 leng5- hun5 , kiam2 thang the-su5 phou3-goa7-lou7 a2-si7 nng7-phou3-lou7 e5 hng7 mah? Chhin-chhiuN7 Chu2 Ia5-sou kong2 ,“ Ai3 toe3 goa2 e5 tioh8 khek ka-ti7 poe7 sip8-ji7-ke3”. Chit-e5 oe7 si7 kong2 m7-thang kiaN kan-khou2 . Siat-su2 na7 e7 chiau3 chit-e5 oe7 lai5 kiaN5 , thang tit-tioh8 bo5-ke3 e5 po2-poe3 . Phi3-ju7 su7, long5, kong, siong, si3-teng2 e5 lang5 . Thak8-chheh-lang5 poe7-chheh toe3 sian-siN chhut-goa7 hng7-hng7; sou2 iau3-kin2 e5 si7 se3-kan phu5-phio3 e5 eng5-kng na7- tiaN7 ,Choh-sit-lang5 bo5 sit-loh8 cheng3 ngou2-kok e5 si5 . Cho3-kang--e5 tioh8 in-khin5. Cho3- seng-li2--e5 bo5 hiam5 lou7 hng7, si3-ke3 ke3-bou5 . Che long2-si7 ai3 tit-tioh8 se3-kan e7 pai7-hoai7 e5 mi