  2.HiaN-ti7 siong5-siong5 hou7 se3-siok8-lang5 hiam5 in put-hau3 phoa3 kong-ma2 , sou2-i2 u7- si5 gi7-lun7 tioh8 chiong pe7-bo2 lai5 hip chit8- e5 siong7 thang kui7 ti7 thiaN-nih8 hou7 lang5 khoaN3 : mng7-khoaN3 chit-e5 hoat-tou7 ho2 a2 m7-ho2 ? 
  Ng5 Tek-phiau sia2 : Goa2 phah-sng3 chit-e5 li2 iah8 si7 liong2-lan5 e5 su7 . Na7 si7 hip-siong7 si7 ho2 i3-su3, hou7 i-e5 kiaN2-sun thang si5-si5 khoaN3-kiN3 chou2-kong e5 bin7; chiau3 an2-ni lai5 siuN7 chiu7 thang chun2 i. Na7-si7 tiau3 ti7 thiaN-tiong lai5 that se3-siok8 lang5 e5 chhui3 , goa2 siuN7 an2-ni boh8-tit hip-siong7 khah tioh8 . KiaN-liau2 ai3 that se3- siok8 lang5 e5 chhui3, ti3-kau3 lian5-lui7 kiaN2-sun. In-ui7 hiaN-ti7 sou2 hak8-sip8 e5 to7-li2 chhian2-poh8, kap se3-siok8 cho3 chhu3-piN , khoai3-khoai3 siu7 iu7-hek8 . U7-e5 thiaN to7-li2 bo5 thong-ke, chham2-chhai2 thiaN to7-li2 e5 li7- khui se3-kan, cho3 kiaN2 e5 chham2-chhai2 ke- lai7 e5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 lau5-teh hit-e5 siong7 chhin-chhiuN7 khoaN3-kiN3 pun2-sin chit8-poaN, choan5-sim che3-su7, pi2 keng3 bok8-chu2 khah siong-tiong7 . Tioh8 siuN7 chai7-cha2 kau3-taN lang5 tauh8-tauh8 eng7 ki5-kha2 e5 ke3-ti3 kiaN- liau2 lang5 chek-pi7 i, kau3 lou7-boe2 be7 hou7 lang5 bo5 chek-pi7. Tioh8 siuN7 Chu2 Ia5-sou in-ui7 lan2 bo5 kiaN lang5 siat-tok8, ai3 siok8 lan2 e5 choe7; ho5-hong3 lan2 u7 choe7 e5 lang5 ng3-bang7 siok8, tu2-tioh8 tam7-poh8 e5 siat- tok8 , kiam2 thang chng-cho3 ki5-kha2 lai5 bian2-tit chek-pi7 . Chong2-si7 ai3 hip pe7-bo2 e5 heng5-siong7 kap ki3 i siN-si2 e5 jit8, goa2 phah-sng3 tioh8 hip, tioh8 ki3 ti7 siau3-phou7 lai5 khng3 ti7 au7-tai7 , bian2-tit be7 ki3--tit . Na7-si7 hip- siong7 tiau3 ti7 thiaN-tiong-nih8 e5 su7, tioh8 chhui2-tok8 si5-se3 thang chun2 , chiaN3 chun2 i. 
  Ngou2-gu7-jian5 sia2: Goa2 ti7 lou7-nih8 chham chit8-e5 boe7 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5 cho3-hoe2 kiaN5 saN-kap tam5-lun7 to7-li2 . I chiu7 kong2 , To7-li2 tak8-hang7 si7 ho2 , chong2-si7 bo5 chiah e5 che3-su7 . Goa2 in3 i kong2 , Che3-su7 u7 sim2-mih8 thang li7-ek chou2-kong a2-bo5 mah ? Eng7 hit-phiN3-a2 chha5 an2-ni bo5 thong ; iah8 si7 oh-tit siu-sip8 , an2-ni m7 ho2- se3 . Sou2-i2 goan2 seng3-kau3 koat-toan3 bo5 beh eng7 chit-ho7 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 liu5-thoan5 , che3- su7 , siat-lip8 sin5-chu2. Goan2 seng3-kau3 e5 lang5 beh lai5 ki3-liam7 pe7-bo2 , tioh8 lai5 hip pe7-bo2 e5 siau2-eng2, soa3 lai5 sia2 pe7-bo2 e5 siN- si5 jit8-goeh8 , koe3-ong2 e5 ni5-sou3 ; soa3 lai5 sia2 pe7-bo2 it-seng e5 lai5-lek8, khin5-khiam7, ho2 tek-heng7 , jiat8-sim sin3 Chu2 pai3 Siong7-te3 , gau5 kiaN5 jin5-ai3, ho2 e5 tou7-liong7, sou2 cho3--e5 thang bian2-le7 i-e5 kiaN2-sun. Chiong i ho2 lau5 teh e5 oe7 siong5-siong5 thang lai5 ka3-si7 kiaN2-sun, oh8 i ho2 e5 bou5-iuN7 . I thiaN-liau2 chiu7 o-lo2 kong2, An2-ni iau2 koh khah ho2 iaN5-koe3 eng7 hit sin5-chu2 lai5 ki3-liam7 pe7-bo2 u7 ban7-poe7 . 
  Lang5 beh hip siau2-eng2 , tioh8 put-chi2 beng5 chiah ho2 . 
  Ngou2-gu7-jian5 ai3 chheng2-kau3 : Lun-kau3 che3-bong7 e5 su7 kaN2 bo5 lang5 iau2-ku2 u7 an2-ni teh kiaN5 . Chong2-si7 hit- ho7 kui3-choa2 m7-chai si7 thang a2 m7-thang , m7-chai si7 siok8 ti7 khian3-sng2 iN7-toan a2-bo5 . 
